name: Haute Couture | Summer Dresses
description:
If you'd like to support me and do more:
https://ko-fi.com/edgonkofi
If you're looking for a >>LoRA Making Tutorial<<

The latest model is a LoHa, make sure to install the Lycoris extension!

GitHub - KohakuBlueleaf/a1111-sd-webui-locon: A extension for loading LyCORIS model in sd-webui

Summer Dresses

While we prepare for the coming of warmer days, I would like to give you all some sunlight and chic in LoRA format. Practical and comfortable, informal, this is a staple of everyday fashion in warm weather.

Here are the Summer dresses!

Download and get yours!
